{"tid":1550392,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[WTF?] 油麻地 23歲男手腳被綁膠袋笠頭 又無可疑","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T16:34:41.000Z","uid":26773,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6cc548dbefb53048116772d46100781d2eab3c68","tid":1550392,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:51:33.000Z","msg":"油麻地劏房揭命案 23歲男手腳被綁膠袋笠頭 警調查指無可疑<br />\n<br />\n今日傍晚6時18 分，警方接獲一名非華裔男子報案，指油麻地上海街113號一個低層劏房單位傳出異味，鄰居報警後，警方及消防登門，爆門入屋後發現一具南亞裔男子屍體倒卧單位內，男死者3歲。警方其後封鎖現場，正調查死亡原因，案件改列屍體發現案處理，由油尖重案組接手。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，警方入屋後，在一張碌架床上發現死者，他頭笠膠袋，一隻手被毛巾綁住，雙腳被膠紙綁起。然而經警方調查後，認為事件無可疑，死者死因有待驗屍確定。至今早（15日）肇事單位已解封，有鄰居指男事主居於上址約4至5個月，近期不見他出入單位，至昨日單位傳出臭味。<br />\n<br />\n有住客指，死者租住在上址一個劏房單位約4至6個月，平時很少見他出入，見面時不會與人交談，所以不認識他。住客又指，死者生前有時在夜晚會大叫，或敲牆。<br />\n<br />\nYAHOO NEWS"},{"pid":"a98fc88ea49baa8bb101db4154850b3d6e29d41f","tid":1550392,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:51:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fac2d2b834bc6526f0fc3a686c1d48562d5099d","tid":1550392,"uid":14958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:53:08.000Z","msg":"3歲定23歲呀"},{"pid":"b2dc430f82b41df9410065f4c1d250d4c844929e","tid":1550392,"uid":160847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:53:29.000Z","msg":"幾撚耐之前呀戇尻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f673436877e4e4d4ad452abe6bad86954fe6cc","tid":1550392,"uid":141641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:53:48.000Z","msg":"3歲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd273870e42c60f8249bba6b514055b9af0bd09","tid":1550392,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:54:10.000Z","msg":"原來DEL左個2字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"378336f0a8f65cf2d8a306fa6b35896c1dd270b8","tid":1550392,"uid":114121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:54:33.000Z","msg":"old news?<br />\n但咁都冇可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食屎啦"},{"pid":"fdd76626f5ff3e3ca4dde51cdc125639bc697f17","tid":1550392,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:54:45.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我警告你班仆街！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽日啲<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國旗</span>唔好周圍掉！<br />\n路邊見到唔該即刻幫手執返！<br />\n完咗活動攞返屋企收藏！</span></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evxvjtB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevxvjtB.jpg&h=73325a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 快啲聽熟加背歌詞，<br />\n唱得莊嚴啲！</span> <a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=9b31ef59\" target=\"